title: NPR Music's No. 1 Albums And Songs Of May
description: At the end of every month, the NPR Music team picks their favorite albums and songs. Their passions vary widely, from  Atlanta rapper Deante' Hitchcock to Australian ambient artist Madeleine Cocolas.
